The paper deals with efficient querying of road networks, which is a problem in database systems (cs.DB). It also involves data structures and algorithms for nearest neighbor search (cs.DS), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.AI) since kNN is a common technique in these fields. Finally, the paper discusses memory-resident implementations, which falls under systems and architecture (cs.SI).
